.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Paul-Mescal-Photo-by-Jeff-Spicer_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Paul-Mescal-Photo-by-Jeff-Spicer_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Paul-Mescal-Photo-by-Jeff-Spicer_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Paul-Mescal-Photo-by-Jeff-Spicer_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>今天（11 月 7 日）在都柏林举行了一场类似<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mescal">保罗·麦斯卡尔的</a>比赛，七名选手角逐一份微薄的奖金。</p><p>参赛者——其中一名并不打算参加活动，只是在上班的路上——突然出现在史密斯菲尔德广场，留着与演员相似的发型，穿着不合时宜的短裤。</p><p>比赛在灯塔电影院外的鹅卵石地上举行，几个小时后，梅斯卡尔本人就出现在了<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/gladiator-ii"><em>《角斗士 II》</em></a>的爱尔兰首映式上。比赛承诺获胜者可以选择一张 20 欧元的支票或三品脱啤酒。 </p><figure id="attachment_3773232" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3773232" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3773232" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Paul-Mescal-in-Gladiator-II.jpg" alt="保罗·梅斯卡尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Paul-Mescal-in-Gladiator-II.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Paul-Mescal-in-Gladiator-II-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Paul-Mescal-in-Gladiator-II-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Paul-Mescal-in-Gladiator-II-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Paul-Mescal-in-Gladiator-II-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Paul-Mescal-in-Gladiator-II-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3773232" class="wp-caption-text"> 《角斗士 II》中的保罗·梅斯卡尔 – 图片来源：派拉蒙</figcaption></figure><p>25 岁的杰克·沃尔·奥莱利 (Jack Wall O&#39;Reilly) 被评选为最像麦斯卡尔酒的人，他对自己的奖励感到非常高兴。</p><p> “我现在正在工作，所以 20 英镑或几品脱就足以度过这一天了，”他告诉<a href="ht